These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: blood-red, black, purple, fuchsia, green, white, yellow
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, canadian, chinese, mexican, nigerian, thai
 1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the chinese##1
 2. the mexican is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 3. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 4. the canadian is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the person who likes purple is in the middle##1
 6. the argentine is on the far left##1
 7. the person who likes green is the argentine##1
 8. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the canadian is on the left of the australian##1
10. the chinese is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
11. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Color           | green | fuchsia | black | purple | blood-red | white | yellow |
| Nationality   | argentine    | mexican   | chinese      | nigerian | canadian    | australian    | thai         |

