.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: cranberry, cucumber, eggplant, nectarine, peach, raspberry, watermelon
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: disaster, epic, musical, satire, adventure, documentary, time-travel
 1. the person watching adventure movies is the person eating nectarine##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the person watching documentary movies is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 5. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 6. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 7. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
10. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | cranberry | cucumber | peach | nectarine | raspberry | watermelon | eggplant |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | musical   | satire   | adventure      | disaster       | time-travel       | documentary     |

