.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
City: liverpool, miami, prague, london, rome, paris, marseilles
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, freelancer, mechanic, photographer, scientist, teacher, writer
 1. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 2. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the writer##1
 3. the freelancer is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 5. the bartender is the person traveling to rome##1
 6. the mechanic is on the right of the freelancer##1
 7. the freelancer is on the left of the mechanic##1
 8. the freelancer is on the right of the photographer##1
 9. the person traveling to paris is the photographer##1
10. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the bartender##1
11. the photographer is in the middle##1
12. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| City   | miami | rome     | prague  | paris       | liverpool       | marseilles  | london   |
| Job    | teacher  | bartender | writer | photographer | freelancer | mechanic | scientist |

