There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, egyptian, indian, indonesian, nigerian, thai
 1. the person watching disaster movies is the australian##1
 2. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 3. the nigerian is on the right of the egyptian##1
 4. the argentine is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 6. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1
 7. the egyptian is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 8. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the person watching documentary movies is the indonesian##1
10. the indonesian is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
11. the thai is the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime    | horror     | martial-arts     | documentary      | time-travel | disaster      | drama     |
| Nationality   | indian | egyptian | nigerian | indonesian | thai | australian | argentine |

