.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, cooking, drawing, gardening, magic-tricks, sudoku, video-games
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, tea, soy-milk, milk
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person drinking milk##1
 2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 5. the person drinking tea is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | cooking | drawing | sudoku     | gardening | video-games | magic-tricks | board-games |
| Beverage     | milk   | hot-chocolate    | tea | soy-milk     | 7up         | iced-tea     | juice        |

