The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, skateboard, tram, trike
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person driving the bus##1
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 5. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
10. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Hobby    | card-games | dancing   | video-games | reading | hiking  | singing | cooking |
| Transport   | ship   | skateboard | bus | tram     | jet-ski | trike | quad-bike   |

