.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, crime, drama, martial-arts, satire, time-travel
7 different games are played: chess, poker, monopoly, billiard, go, mah-jongg, backgammon
 1. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 3. the person watching time-travel movies is the person playing billiard##1
 4. the person playing go is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 5. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 7. the person playing chess is the person watching crime movies##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the person playing chess is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | time-travel | drama | martial-arts | satire     | animation | crime |
| Game     | mah-jongg | billiard      | backgammon | monopoly    | go | poker   | chess  |

