 4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 6. the person traveling to boston is the person driving the roller##1
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 9. the person traveling to edinburgh is in the middle##1
10. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| City       | venice   | paris | hamburg | edinburgh | prague     | boston | marseilles |
| Transport   | quad-bike | taxi      | boat        | train         | helicopter | roller     | scooter |

