 3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 4. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 5. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left##1
 6. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 8. the person eating strawberry is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
10. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |     5      |     6      |    7     |
| Food   | pumpkin    | orange    | kiwi   | strawberry | grapefruit | watermelon | potato   |
| Sport    | surfing | ice-hockey | tennis | basketball  | volleyball       | rugby     | water-polo |

