 3. the person eating potato is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is the person eating pepper##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is the person eating raspberry##1
 6. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
 7. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 8. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is in the middle##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
12. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |   4    |     5     |    6    |   7    |
| Food          | raspberry | lime     | spinach | pepper | peas      | tomato  | potato |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | iced-tea | cola  | coffee | juice | almond-milk | sprite   |

